author: humbedooh
msg: mod_lua: Redesign the table construction/access mechanism, so we pass on a struct with the request_rec, the table pointer and the table name instead of just the table pointer. This allows us to use the request_rec for logging/editing purposes, as well as inform the user which exact table in the request_rec was modified.
